    • incrementProximities

      public void incrementProximities(DataTuple tuple)
      Store indices of tuples in leaf nodes. Used to calculate RForest proximities (https://www.stat.berkeley.edu/~breiman/RandomForests/cc_home.htm#prox).
      Parameters:
      tuple -

    • predictWeightedAndGetLeafTuples

      public ClusStatistic predictWeightedAndGetLeafTuples(DataTuple tuple, List<Integer> leafTuples) throws ClusException
      Make prediction and store indices of tuples which ended in the same leaf as the given tuple in the leafTuples variable. This is used to calculate RForest proximities https://www.stat.berkeley.edu/~breiman/RandomForests/cc_home.htm#prox
      Parameters:
      tuple - Tuple to predict
      leafTuples - hash codes of tuples which are in the same leaf where the tuple ended will be stored in this variable.
      Throws:
      ClusException

    • printTreeToPythonScriptIterative

      public final void printTreeToPythonScriptIterative(PrintWriter writer, String prefix, HashMap<String,Integer> dict)
      The iterative version of the method for printing Python code. This should be called only at the root node of the tree. Two stages:
      • create hash map node: number of visits, of all nodes in the tree
      • perform depth first search and print Python trees
      Parameters:
      writer -
      prefix -
      dict -
